        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Kingston Jamaica</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>Janry 7th 1859</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dear <addressee>Leeser</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I have received your esteemed<lb/> favor together with the books
                which I shall<lb/> endeavor to dispose of as early as<lb/> possible. I understand
                that a <persName>Mr. Joseph</persName><lb/> is selling books of the same description
                at<lb/> $2 piece, however, I shall do the best I can<lb/> for you, so that you shall
                not <sic>loose</sic> by them<lb/> it will not answer for me to send the first nos of
                the magazine to any one as is customary with<lb/> your publishers for I will not
                suffer any book<lb/> to go out of my hands without the cash being paid<lb/> for them
                as there is no dependence on any one in<lb/>
                <placeName>Jamaica</placeName>. Nothing but Poverty every where, I<lb/> notice the
                different deaths and except <persName>Mrs. <del>Hk</del><lb/> Hackenburgh</persName>
                is what <persName>Lex Liebe<add>?</add></persName>, give my<lb/> love to
                    <persName>Louisa</persName>, and say I have received her letter<lb/> but could
                not answer by this opportunity.</p>
            <p>Remember me kindly to <persName>Mrs. Cousens</persName> &amp; the<lb/> family,
                    <del>In</del> as well as all friends. In the hope<lb/> that you are completely
                recoverd &amp; enjoying health</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I remain <add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Your friend</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">A. C. Peirpotte</persName>
            </p>
            <p>The book given as a sample<lb/> was the same as those sent now.<lb/>
                <add>?</add>
                <persName>LD Lufus<add>?</add></persName> remembers<lb/> Kindly to you all.</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <addressee>Reverend Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">pr <persName>William Thompson</persName></p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">via <placeName>New Orleans</placeName></p>
        </body>
